metadata.description: A new ongoing series from the creative team who brought you the hit TECH JACKET DIGITAL mini! Zack Thompson: community college drop out, lives with his parents... This is who protects us from what lies beyond our world?! But he's also Tech Jacket, the self-styled "Galactic Guardian of Earth," and when a big-ass space ship enters Earth's orbit, Zack will face the greatest challenge of his life!
metadata.name: Tech Jacket (2014- )
